{"tid":1556872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地依家嘅 「拉攏/說服式文宣」 夠唔夠？","createTime":"2019-09-10T01:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:26:47.000Z","uid":138409,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fc68453cf4370579cbbf187496ed0ea3d16108","tid":1556872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"運動初期我地有「保民生反修例」大聯盟、扮藍絲、爭取中間派支持<br />\n甚至乎有整長輩圖、google聲影片之類<br />\n<br />\n但係最近嘅文宣似乎比較少見呢類型，比較多係針對己方嘅hardcore支持者<br />\n（至少就我所見就少左，假如有的話求指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n文宣對己方固然有打氣作用，但係最重要嘅應該係對淺黃、淺藍嘅群眾<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想做民意L，但係鞏固己方支持係無時無刻都應該做嘅嘢，尤其是每次前線有比較明顯嘅武力行為（不論對物定對人）嘅時候。<span style=\"color: gold;\">我覺得文宣唔單止要追究警暴/渲染己方嘅形象；<em>每一次使用比較明顯嘅武力之後，應該要追加文宣解釋點解咁做</em>（例如毀損港鐵設施之類）</span> 說服嘅對象當然唔係深藍，而係某啲可能因為己方武力而退卻嘅民眾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqdF06T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqdF06T.jpg&h=ae7218da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你有睇立場、港台之類新聞嘅fb留言區<br />\n你見每次都有部分己方支持者 好心咁樣將扔汽油彈/毀損公物賴去黑警臥底到，就知道呢啲行為就算係己方陣營，都唔係所有人都能夠立即接受同埋理解（當然我相信有啲係臥底所為；但肯定有啲係前線手足），而我地嘅文宣正正係要針對呢班人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">依家黑警濫暴，某程度上係為我地提供彈藥，但係呢場運動繼續走下去，單靠對家犯錯係唔夠㗎；<strong>我地自己都需要有論述支持點解響某次行動當中使用武力，係有正當性</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地嘅行動（對比6月9日）肯定係升級左；但係文宣追唔追得上？<br />\n<br />\n求各位指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ecb76ee9f1e8a392345c6ec134bb57017c2c9f","tid":1556872,"uid":146737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=909e8621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"a3dc4d38c47e4b32736c10f65f12c656614cd388","tid":1556872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"對於中大有關武力使用嘅民調<br />\n有人有唔同詮釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067091&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=34b4daf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067091&h=52b21223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067091</a><br />\n<br />\n另外上述#1觀點<br />\n係受到尋日好青年荼毒室響中大搞嘅罷課講座啟發，謹此致謝"},{"pid":"fc35fbc30835c1a85f96c2344e9911022292d2ed","tid":1556872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ecb76ee9f1e8a392345c6ec134bb57017c2c9f","tid":1556872,"uid":146737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https: